text: inanite yamenachihu sewochi hoyi! sētochini yasigededachihu ẖonachihu litiwerisuna gilits’ini met’ifo šira kališeru besitek’eri keset’achiḫwachewi kefīluni litiwesidu litagulalwachewimi le’inanite āyifek’edimi፡፡ bemelikamimi tenwanwaruwachewi፡፡ bitit’eluwachewimi (tagesu)፡፡ ānidachini negeri bitit’elu ālahimi be’irisu bizu degi negerini līyaderigi yichalalina፡፡
